  "title": "Cherry Cream",
  "handle": "cherry-cream",
  "body_html": "<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">A bold, juicy cherry twist </span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">What you’ll smell:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>It opens with a burst of rich cherry—slightly tart but quickly turning syrupy and sweet. Then the signature coffee note comes in, giving it that dark, slightly bitter edge that balances the sweetness. As it dries down, it becomes warm and creamy with vanilla wrapping everything together, leaving a seductive, dessert-like trail with a hint of spice.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">Notes:</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Top: Cherry accord</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Heart: Coffee, orange blossom</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Base: Vanilla, patchouli</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">Vibe:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>Sultry, confident, and a little mysterious. Think red lips, night lights, and a statement outfit.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">When to wear:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>Perfect for nights out, dinners, and special occasions. Best in fall and summer nights if you want something bold and attention-grabbing.</span></p>",
